OL,3,CHeathrow Airport releases iconic
OL,4,Cphotos to celebrate 80th anniversary
OL,6,FAs Heathrow has grown in size so too
OL,7,Fhas the number of people transiting
OL,8,Fthrough it. Some 63,000 passengers
OL,9,Fpassed through Heathrow during its
OL,10,Ffirst year compared to 84.5 million
OL,11,Flast year.
OL,13,FThe airport has beared witness to some
OL,14,Fof the country's most memorable
OL,15,Fmoments, and in celebration of its
OL,16,Flatest milestone, has released a
OL,17,Fseries of photographs that capture its
OL,18,F80-year history.
OL,20,FOpening Year
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
