OL,3,CHeathrow Airport releases iconic
OL,4,Cphotos to celebrate 80th anniversary
OL,6,FNearly a century ago, Heathrow's
OL,7,Fterminals were former military
OL,8,Fmarquees and not the grand buildings
OL,9,Fmany will be well accustomed with
OL,10,Ftoday.
OL,12,FThe facilities were basic but
OL,13,Fcomfortable and equipped with
OL,14,Ffloralpatterned armchairs, settees
OL,15,Fand small tables containing vases of
OL,16,Ffresh flowers.
OL,18,FPassengers even walked across wooden
OL,19,Fduckboards to protect their footwear
OL,20,Ffrom the muddy airfield as they
OL,21,Freached their aircraft.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
