OL,3,CHeathrow Airport releases iconic
OL,4,Cphotos to celebrate 80th anniversary
OL,6,FQueen Returns Home
OL,8,FPrincess Elizabeth was on a overseas
OL,9,Ftour of Kenya when it was announced
OL,10,Fthat King George VI had died on
OL,11,FFebruary 6, 1952.
OL,13,FShe instantly became Queen Elizabeth
OL,14,FII upon her father's death - the first
OL,15,Fmonarch to accede to the throne while
OL,16,Fabroad in more than 200 years.
OL,18,FThe new Queen cut short her trip and
OL,19,Freturned home, flying into Heathrow
OL,20,Fthe following day dressed in all black.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
