OL,3,CHeathrow Airport releases iconic
OL,4,Cphotos to celebrate 80th anniversary
OL,6,FThe Beatles' Euphoric Return
OL,8,FBeatlemania was at its pomp in the
OL,9,F1960s, and the return of the iconic
OL,10,FBritish pop act to the UK in 1964,
OL,11,Ffollowing their hugely successful US
OL,12,Ftour, epitomised their almost
OL,13,Fubiquitous popularity.
OL,15,FThousands of fans greeted the quartet
OL,16,Fof Ringo Starr, John Lennon, George
OL,17,FHarrison and Paul McCartney, when they
OL,18,Fstepped onto the Heathrow runway.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
