OL,3,CHeathrow Airport releases iconic
OL,4,Cphotos to celebrate 80th anniversary
OL,6,FSuch was the fandom for Concorde, that
OL,7,Fone passenger - Bob Ingham - saved for
OL,8,Fthree years to buy his ticket for the
OL,9,Fmaiden flight from Heathrow.
OL,11,FFast forward 27 years and British
OL,12,FAirways carried out the final Concorde
OL,13,Fflight from the airport's Terminal 1.
OL,15,FGlory For England Rugby
OL,17,FVictory for England at the 2003 Rugby
OL,18,FWorld Cup, in Australia, sparked
OL,19,Fjubilant scenes of celebrations back
OL,20,Fhome.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
