OL,3,CHeathrow Airport releases iconic
OL,4,Cphotos to celebrate 80th anniversary
OL,6,FThe team were serenaded with chants of
OL,7,F'Swing Low, Sweet Chariot' by
OL,8,Fthousands of fans, when they arrived
OL,9,Fat Terminal 4 on November 25, 2003.
OL,11,FCovid Standstill
OL,13,FA ban on all non-essential travel by
OL,14,Fthe government due to the Covid
OL,15,Fpandemic in March 2020 saw Heathrow
OL,16,Fbecome a virtual ghost-town overnight.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
